<sect2>
<title>Installation de <application>GStreamer</application></title>

<para>Installez <application>GStreamer</application> en lançant les commandes suivantes&nbsp;:</para>

<screen><userinput><command>./configure --prefix=`pkg-config --variable=prefix ORBit-2.0` \
    --localstatedir=/var/lib --sysconfdir=/etc/gnome \
    --disable-docs-build &amp;&amp;
make &amp;&amp;
make install &amp;&amp;
gst-register</command></userinput></screen>

</sect2>
